          <h2>Welcome!</h2>
          <p>My name is Adam Hobaugh. I am the Tech Coordinator, a member of the Webteam and the primary web developer for the Department of Computer Science at the University of Pittsburgh.</p> 
          <p>Each member of the CS Department receives some webspace when they get their accounts. I debated for a while on what to put here. Should it be all work? Should it be all play? Well, we all know what they say about devoting something to one thing. So, I decided I would do a little of each.</p>
          <div class="split">
            <div class="split_col1">
            <h4>Work</h4>
            <p>First the work, if you have any issues regarding the CS Department's technical resources or website, please go to <a href="http://tech.cs.pitt.edu/tickets/send">http://tech.cs.pitt.edu/tickets/send</a> to submit a help ticket.
            </p>
            <p>
              Some useful resources for the department are:
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <a href="http://tech.cs.pitt.edu/">
