              <p>I am also an active member in the Pittsburgh Pagan Community. When I was a student, I had no idea that Pittsburgh had a pagan community, let alone anyone other than me at Pitt. If you are a pagan student and feel that you are alone at Pitt, please feel free to contact me and I can put you in contact with the community.</p>
